comments: Mathurin (IND) cuts across the perimeter and marginal contact occurs with Smart (BOS) as the defenders switch.
Brown (BOS) does not maintain legal guarding position and makes contact with Haliburton's (IND) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Brown (BOS) is already in Mathurin's (IND) path and marginal contact occurs as Brown releases from the contact.
Hield (IND) is moving alongside Tatum's (BOS) path and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Haliburton (IND) legally contests Tatum's (BOS) driving shot attempt.
Brown (BOS) cleanly deflects the ball away from Mathurin (IND) during rebounding.
Horford (BOS) is moving alongside Hield's (IND) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Mathurin (IND) and Brogdon (BOS) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Mathurin (IND) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact from Tatum (BOS) as he passes the ball.
Hield (IND) is already in Smart's (BOS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Turner (IND) is already in Smart's (BOS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Horford (BOS) legally contests Haliburton's (IND) jump shot attempt.
Tatum (BOS) clamps and holds Turner's (IND) arm and affects his ability to pursue the rebound.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Brown (BOS) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to Indiana.
Brogdon (BOS) brings his hand towards Mathurin's (IND) front and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Haliburton (IND) is bracing for the contact from Smart (BOS) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away from the contact.
Smart (BOS) does not maintain verticality and his right arm makes contact with Haliburton's (IND) arm during his jump shot attempt.
Nembhard (IND) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot and he legally lifts his pivot foot to pass.
Smart (BOS) moves somewhat forward towards Hield's (IND) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Tatum (BOS) saves the ball back in bounds before his foot lands out of bounds.
Smart (BOS) swipes his hand down and makes contact with Nesmith's (IND) arm as he defends the shot near the rim.
Brown (BOS) brings his hands towards Haliburton (IND) and marginal contact occurs as Brown releases away to secure the pass.
Haliburton (IND) establishes his right foot as his pivot foot and he maintains his pivot foot after his gather.

Replay review of the foul called on Horford (BOS) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Horford does not maintain verticality and makes contact with Haliburton's (IND) arm during his shot near the rim.
Brown (BOS) and Nesmith (IND) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Nembhard (IND) places his hand momentarily on Tatum's (BOS) side before correcting.
Tatum (BOS) is already in Haliburton's (IND) path and marginal contact occurs as the defenders switch.
Haliburton (IND) does not maintain legal guarding position and makes contact with Tatum's (BOS) arm as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Horford (BOS) legally contests Nesmith's (IND) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Brogdon (BOS) avoids making contact with Haliburton (IND) during his jump shot.
